project:
Hey, there's a block of ice in the way of our delivery bot. Please melt it!

(Also, click anywhere when you're ready to wake up the bot.)

Alright, let's do the opposite now.

If you freeze the water, our bot could get across.

If you don't have anything to freeze, make it rain.

Literally.

Be careful not to melt the ice when our bot is going across it.

You don't want it to fall down, do you?

If you're aiming for that sweet A grade, you'd better not mess the order of your weather changes.

Just a tip.

Seriously, don't change the weather more times than needed or you won't get a high grade.

Trust me, it matters.

Hot tip: plants like the sun. It makes them grow super fast.

I read that in the Gardening for Absolute Dummies.

And the thing that makes flowers bloom? You wouldn't believe it.

IT'S WATER!

On the other hand, cold is not something that flowers like.

That's something we've got in common.
Hang on there, it's almost over.

This one looks like a real doozy.

But it's the last one, I promise!
